{"tid":114690,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"前中學教師彭聲朗　將軍澳失蹤","createTime":"2017-02-10T03:21:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-11T03:14:14.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6989124c41a42f68c86f06d669bbf79585915905","tid":114690,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T03:21:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19924085&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170210\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19924085%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170210&d=oAUO7kpDmgkuxlfprI4EYS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=21b0fa39\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19924085%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170210&h=872f642c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19924085&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170210</a><br />\n<br />\n前中學教師彭聲朗　將軍澳失蹤<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】29歲男子彭聲朗，前日凌晨離開將軍澳寶康路住所後失蹤，由於他曾向家人透露尋死之意，家人擔心不已，報警求助。<br />\n<br />\n警方呼籲市民，如有事主消息可致電3661 0316，或電郵至rmpu-ke-2@police.gov.hk￼，與東九龍總區失蹤人口調查組或任何一間警署聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n彭聲朗身高約1.8米，體重約63公斤，瘦身材、方形面、黃皮膚及蓄短黑髮。他最後露面時身穿黑色長袖上衣、淺色長褲及深色鞋。<br />\n<br />\n彭於城大畢業後曾在一所中學任教，喜歡打籃球及行山，曾在facebook分享如何改善不開心情緒。他指出，不開心時可嘗試在房間收拾東西，並問自己，有那些所珍惜的東西是很久沒有拿出來看過，然後發現「其實沒有甚麼是放不下的，因為你根本不知在哪時已經放下了」。<br />\n<br />\n上一則:&nbsp;四驅撞單車腳踏失控　追撞Audi再翻側<br />\n<br />\n下一則:&nbsp;昨晚六合彩開獎結果"},{"pid":"1bf85c67feb086fd683924e9e5e1c3bb7f349cca","tid":114690,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T03:36:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e384d22832c0dd297812d5ce59c26cb20943765","tid":114690,"uid":40940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T03:39:55.000Z","msg":"中意教人諗思想要正面，正能量撚先易死"},{"pid":"f471cf4d19de3269a0dbdbeee8fb4fc5a5fa0e94","tid":114690,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T03:40:55.000Z","msg":"昨晚六合彩開獎結果呢"},{"pid":"cb68479a9753106ca6c67d8e660ed4ceaed7c0cb","tid":114690,"uid":83853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T03:45:17.000Z","msg":"返屋企啦， 唔好做傻事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85322880727e312eb27244b26265db519ef90023","tid":114690,"uid":3773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T06:00:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec94f16e6848f29af29768a890a627255c583afa","tid":114690,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T06:02:38.000Z","msg":"還掂D死因生平都係報紙佬作出黎"},{"pid":"80342bcdddf18b928602b845f75a8bb23d9b8686","tid":114690,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T06:48:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ed4bad6e5ce496948cca1528a15f803f019aaa35","tid":114690,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T06:52:38.000Z","msg":"「其實沒有甚麼是放不下的，因為你根本不知在哪時已經放下了」。"},{"pid":"d7c134333ef7ad780726dce1b42f239375a61768","tid":114690,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T06:54:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c064298b31d8cf566fc6e2d0e5fc1de59d0625dd","tid":114690,"uid":25899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T07:18:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>「其實沒有甚麼是放不下的，因為你根本不知在哪時已經放下了」。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ada2346b434fe948770f062655ce9a6a9627de2","tid":114690,"uid":62226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T08:16:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中意教人諗思想要正面，正能量撚先易死</blockquote><br />\